00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,710
Eunuch Qin.

430
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:23,760
Your Grace.

431
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:27,520
Lord Xue.

432
00:21:27,950 --> 00:21:31,110
