00:39:08,020 --> 00:39:11,700
♪Life is long but love isn’t♪

813
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:15,050
♪There’s regret in the world♪

814
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:17,660
♪Only with you around♪

815
00:39:17,720 --> 00:39:22,160
♪We’ll never lose contact♪

